<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="自学成才的建筑鬼才：日本顶尖设计师安藤忠雄（下）" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366265" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/qrdesignhistory.jpg" alt="用一篇超全面的文章，帮你完整梳理哥特风格发展史" width="180" height="180" /></span></p>
